---
title: Mexican-Spiced Chickpea & Roast Potato Bowl with Avocado Salad, Corn Chips & Plant-Based Mayo
description: A Mexican-style bowl is fun and very tasty, so we made a veggie option too because these chickpeas are too good
when cooked in an enchilada sauce and Tex-Mex spices. Add in an avocado salsa then dunk in those corn chips to
collect a little of everything in one bite.
